                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8704" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0938</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1417 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宽邦科技：人工智能浪潮下量化投资的技术平权之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Kuangbang Technology: The Path to Technological Democratization in Quantitative Investment Under the Wave of Artificial Intelligence</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高洁，谭慧敏(通讯作者)，张雅瑄，罗崇登，王鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成都宽邦科技有限公司 </td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新管理；量化投资；人工智能；大语言模型；技术平权；2024百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Innovation Management; Quantitative Investment; AI; Large Language Model; Technological Democratization </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">宽邦科技由梁举于2016年创立，致力于通过人工智能推动量化投资的技术平权。公司最初开发了StockRanker算法，并建立了AI量化社区平台，以降低普通用户的入门门槛。随后，宽邦科技推出了更易用的量化平台“BigQuant”，通过简化用户界面和提供教程，扩大了市场接受度。在商业模式创新方面，宽邦科技与中信证券等企业合作，提供定制化量化解决方案。公司还敏锐地捕捉到人工智能生成内容(AIGC)技术的潮流，整合ChatGPT技术推出了专属量化金融模型“QuantChat”，从而提升用户体验和决策效率。此外，通过与高校和政府的合作，宽邦科技推动了量化金融知识的普及并构建了一个创新管理生态系统。在中国的特定市场情境下，宽邦科技通过持续的技术创新和新产品开发管理，不断优化和拓展其量化投资工具，有效缩小了技术鸿沟并促进了社会公平。本案例详细探索了宽邦科技在新产品开发管理、AI情景下的创新管理及AIGC领域的应用，特别强调了如何通过商业模式创新实现技术平权和技术的广泛可获取性，确保技术发展的利益能广泛惠及社会各界。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Established in 2016 by Liang Ju, Kuangbang Technology aims to democratize quantitative investment through the application of artificial intelligence (AI). Initially, the company developed the StockRanker algorithm and established an AI-driven community platform to lower the entry barriers for average users. Subsequently, Kuangbang Technology introduced &quot;BigQuant,&quot; a more user-friendly quantitative platform that simplifies the user interface and offers tutorials, thus broadening its market acceptance. The company has innovated its business model through collaborations with firms like CITIC Securities to provide customized quantitative solutions. Additionally, Kuangbang Technology has embraced AI-generated content (AIGC) technology, integrating it with ChatGPT to launch the specialized financial model &quot;QuantChat,&quot; enhancing user experience and decision-making efficiency. Moreover, in partnership with universities and government agencies, the company has promoted the widespread understanding of quantitative finance and developed an innovative management ecosystem. Within the context of China’s market and regulatory environment, Kuangbang Technology continuously refines and expands its quantitative investment tools through ongoing technological innovation and new product development management, effectively narrowing the technological divide and fostering social equity. This case study thoroughly explores Kuangbang Technology&#39;s strategies in new product development management, innovation management under AI scenarios, and AIGC applications, highlighting how business model innovation can achieve technological equity and widespread access, ensuring that the benefits of technological advancements reach all sectors of society.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《管理伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术平权；社会责任；普惠性创新；商业模式创新；数字技术驱动创新管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
